report_precision_derate(25.10)                  report_precision_derate(25.10)

Name
       report_precision_derate

Syntax
       report_precision_derate <integer >

       Default: 3

       Controls the number of digits appearing after the decimal point in der-
       ate values in the timing report output.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

